From: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <acme@redhat.com>
Date: Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:12:13 -0300
Subject: perf ftrace latency: Introduce --min-latency to narrow down into a
 latency range
Git-commit: 08b875b6bf6085894f5cc65e028ae76f371a805e
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Things below and over will be in the first and last, outlier, buckets.

Without it:

